Once upon a time, there lived a restless mouse in an upside-down house. One day, this curious mouse left his cozy and quiet home and found a mysterious castle. Wandering this castle, he found a strange-and-little sword stuck in a strange-and-little stone. He tugged on this sword with all his might, and was flung into an adventure with magic, danger, and friendship.

After completing his final quest, he wishes to go back to his upside-down house to finally rest. He returns back to that castle to put back his strange-and-little sword back in that strange-and-little stone. 

Now along the long and winding road he goes…
===
